Package: multifer
Title: Typed Perturbation Inference for Projector-Based Multivariate Models
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Bradley",
           family = "Buchsbaum",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com")
Description: A shape-first inference layer for projector-based multivariate
    models. Provides one coherent system for component significance,
    variable and score stability, and subspace uncertainty across one-block,
    cross-block, multiblock, and generalized-eigen shapes. Built around
    typed shapes (geometry, relation, design), strict dispatch, machine-
    enforced validity contracts, and latent-unit-centered output schemas.
